sql_json.natural_language: Show me the newest email that includes julie@lineagecoffee.com and accounts@toscant.co.za together.
sql_json.generated_sql: SELECT messageId, threadId, fromEmail, subject, sentAt, snippet FROM email_search_index WHERE 'julie' IN UNNEST(toPeople) AND 'accounts@toscant.co.za' IN UNNEST(toEmails) ORDER BY sentAt DESC LIMIT 1;
